(Software tools, and the game engine internals. You can read a preview on Google Books and buy) Tj
T*
(it here: Amazon.com \(.fr, .de, .co.uk, .ca,...\). Google Play Books for web browsers, Android) Tj
T*
(devices, and iOS devices. It took me three years to complete this project. It had its fair) Tj
T*
(share of heavy winds and bumpy roads. I thought it could benefit some writers in the making to) Tj
T*
(give a postmortem and share what I learned in the process. More...) Tj
